## Overview

When you need something to shatter, break, crumble, or succumb to the rigors of battle, **Destructible Actors** are a good way to go. With a host in in-editor tools and support for **PhysX APEX Destruction** assets, Unreal Engine 4 offers many ways for content creators to build and ultimately destroy their worlds.

